36+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572543556"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572543556"&gt;廣州英文名，叫Kwong Chau&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt; &lt;!-- google_ad_section_end --&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content><link href="https://www.discuss.com.hk/viewthread.php?tid=31936713&amp;extra=page%3D1%26amp%3Bfilter%3D0%26amp%3Borderby%3Ddateline%26amp%3Bascdesc%3DDESC&amp;tr_h=2049023388683185b3cd1d33_98389435"/><published>2025-05-24T15:48:36+08:00</published></entry><entry><id>9e025512ac598a8bd3607914347210ef</id><title>川西四個轆🚗10天遊記分享</title><updated>2025-04-28T13:12:47+08:00</updated><author><name>uncle9nine</name></author><content type="html">&lt;p&gt;Published on: 2025-04-28T13:12:47+0800&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;div class="postmessage-content t_msgfont" id="postmessage_572163997"&gt;&lt;!-- google_ad_section_start --&gt;&lt;span id="postorig_572163997"&gt;今次是第一次在廣東省之外的地方玩自駕遊，而川西是最期待的路線之一，今次小試牛刀玩川西小環線&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16182485" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572163997" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250428/20250428_7a8a701726926953e3d7cRC9ZJkt8Yvw.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/4f3d8e/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250428/20250428_7a8a701726926953e3d7cRC9ZJkt8Yvw.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16182485_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16182485&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Screenshot_2025-04-28-11-06-50-648_com.autonavi.minimap.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (1.1 MB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-4-28 13:12&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/img&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;今次旅程最擔心就是天氣，因為到出發時川西康定那邊仲落緊雪&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;⛄&lt;/span&gt;，一來擔心危險，二來擔心堵車，雖然我在日本都試個幾次雪駕，但大陸唔興雪胎這東西，只能夠裝防滑鏈，而防滑鏈裝除都比較麻煩，所以我在淘X買了防滑輪胎套送去天府機場附近取，有備無患，最后冇用到&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🤣&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;而玩川西自駕遊，租車首選一定越野車&lt;span style="font-size:22px;"&gt;🚙&lt;/span&gt;，因為川西有些路況都比較差，車有四驅，車身高，最重要打卡影相一流&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16182487" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572163997" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250428/20250428_cb2c65ed84988c87d577N9Orq2RtXK0E.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/491ca2/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250428/20250428_cb2c65ed84988c87d577N9Orq2RtXK0E.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16182487_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16182487&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMG_20250415_104523.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (2.74 MB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-4-28 13:12&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;而今次川西行程都高海扙，在出發前一星期都食定紅景天防高反，到當地再買定幾支氧氣吸，結果都有輕微高反，頭有些痛而已，而同行有一個朋友事前冇食，高反比較嚴重&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;以下各地方海拔&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16182486" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572163997" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250428/20250428_9a6993bc01fa75d57b80WtRmfWthonp3.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/e64e57/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250428/20250428_9a6993bc01fa75d57b80WtRmfWthonp3.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16182486_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16182486&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMG_20250428_120832.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (1.19 MB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-4-28 13:12&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;航班&lt;br/&gt;cx 香港~成都天府機場&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;租車&lt;br/&gt;一hi 機場租機場還，車款坦克300&lt;br/&gt;9天租金連全險¥2817&lt;br/&gt;10天行程共行1500km，油費¥1500&lt;br/&gt;etc 費¥363&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;12/4-21/4 行程如下: &lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;12Apr&lt;br/&gt;成都天府機場~2015自貢燈會&lt;br/&gt;住自貢&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16182488" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572163997" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250428/20250428_80e06c44a211d8a7a7cf4eycmLhw4j0r.jpg"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/f97e68/f/800x0/https://img.discuss.com.hk/attachments/day_250428/20250428_80e06c44a211d8a7a7cf4eycmLhw4j0r.jpg"/&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="t_attach" id="attach_16182488_menu" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img alt="" border="0" class="absmiddle" src="images/attachicons/image.gif"/&gt; &lt;a href="attachment.php?aid=16182488&amp;amp;nothumb=yes" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IMG_20250412_200237.jpg&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt; (2.27 MB)&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="t_smallfont"&gt;2025-4-28 13:12&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;br/&gt;13,Apr&lt;br/&gt;自貢~娥媚山&lt;br/&gt;住雅安市&lt;br/&gt;&lt;span id="attach_16182489" onmouseover="showMenu(this.id, 0, 1)" style="position: absolute; display: none"&gt;&lt;img border="0" src="images/discuss_style/attachimg.gif"/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;div class="post-img-container" data-pid="572163997" original-img="https://img.discuss.com.